# Test Reliability

## Waits & Assertions

- No hard waits — never use `page.waitForTimeout()` or `cy.wait(<number>)`; rely on auto-waiting
- Prefer web-first, auto-retrying assertions (e.g. `expect(locator).toBeVisible()`) over manual reads

## Isolation

- Each test must be fully isolated and order-independent; it sets up and tears down its own state/data

## Determinism

- Tests must be deterministic — no branching on application state
